snippet.title: Wanderstop - Reveal Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
Wanderstop is a narrative-centric cozy game about change and tea. Playing as a fallen fighter named Alta, you’ll manage a tea shop within a magical forest and tend to the customers who pass through. But Alta does not want to be here. And if she gets her way, the tea shop will be nothing but a brief and painful memory. Coming soon to PS5.
 
 #ps5 #ps5games
